    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional 2012 Porsche 911 Carrera in Basalt Black Metallic over a Sand Beige leather interior. This vehicle is the definition of 'mint,' having been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage since new. The exterior paint retains its deep, glass-like luster with zero rock chips or swirl marks, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the leather remains supple and matte, free of the typical bolster wear or sun fading found in cars of this vintage. Every button and switch functions with factory precision, and the cabin still carries that distinct new-Porsche aroma. Mechanically, this Carrera is beyond reproach. It comes with a complete binder of service records from authorized dealerships, including a major service recently completed ahead of schedule. The undercarriage is as clean as the body, and the Michelin Pilot Sport tires have less than 500 miles on them. This is a collector-grade example for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection. Two keys, original window sticker, and all manuals included.",
      "price": 48500.0,
